data.description: LOCATION, LOCATION, LOCATION!!!  Stop the car and hop in a golf cart to your dream home! This 4 bedroom / 2 bathroom home boasts over 2,000 sq ft and will tick every box on your home buying checklist. 3336 Crestview Lane is conveniently located within walking distance of dining, shopping, medical appts. and Tiger Point Golf Club. Not much of a golfer? Bring out your water toys because you will be living a short mile away from Oriole Beach Boat Ramp, where you can set sail into Santa Rosa Sound and drift over to Pensacola Beach, Ft. Pickens, or even the Gulf of Mexico. After a long day of having fun in the Florida sun, come back to your amazing Tiger Point home for sunset drinks on your 400 sq ft back deck, partially covered with a beautiful lanai, designed for all types of entertaining. If you want to escape the heat but not miss your party, step inside to your 300 sq ft tiled sunroom with fans. In addition, there is a large, tiled home office that faces the backyard with grand windows that let in the Florida sun. Pass through the double French doors and you will find the master bedroom and ensuite with walk-in closet and double sink with separate water closet and shower. There are two full bathrooms, each has been updated with fresh shower/tub combos and tiled shower walls. There are 3 additional bedrooms, each of which have large windows and are over 120 sq ft. All bedrooms and living areas have been updated with beautiful luxury flooring. The kitchen has double Blanco deep sinks, concrete countertops, hop up dining, and new warranted stainless-steel appliances. The HVAC has been updated and utilizes UV light to help filter the air. The roof and garage door have been recently replaced and are also warranted. Make an appointment today to view this one-of-a-kind dream home!
